  :language: cpp
  :caption: Tables

  Modify the active code below so that it outputs the power of two
  up to 65536, which is :math:`2^{16}`. If you get stuck, you can
  reveal the extra problem at the end for help.
  ~~~~
  #include <iostream>
  #include <cmath>
  using namespace std;

  int main() {
      double x = 1.0;
      while (x < 100.0) {
          cout << x << "\t" << log(x) / log(2.0) << endl;
          x = x * 2.0;
      }
  }